title: Y$_{3}$Al$_{5}$O$_{12}$ Garnet (YAG) Structure
comments:
This is the ternary form of \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B3C12D3_cI160_230_a_c_h_d-001}{garnet}. As with other forms of garnet the there are frequent substitutions on all sites. 
 In the measured sample, 1.3\% of the yttrium is replaced by dysprosium.
